      "achievedLevel": 3,
      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "QOIs used in validation must directly correspond to the hemolysis index quantities specified in project requirements for the VAD COU; surrogate QOIs must be formally justified.",
      "rationale": "The normalized index of hemolysis (NIH) was used as the primary QOI, which is relevant but not identical to the modified index of hemolysis (MIH) specified in project requirements. Achieved level 3 is below required level 4."
    },
