      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Validation experiments must be conducted on the same or geometrically similar pump under conditions representative of the VAD COU as specified in project requirements.",
      "rationale": "Validation was performed on the FDA benchmark pump geometry, which is geometrically similar but not identical to the target VAD pump. Operating conditions partially overlap the COU envelope. Achieved level 2 is substantially below required level 4."
