      "acceptanceCriteria": "The hemolysis damage model form (power-law vs. mechanistic) must be formally justified against project requirements and literature; sensitivity to model form selection must be quantified.",
      "rationale": "The Giersiepen-Wurzinger power-law model was used without formal justification of model form selection or sensitivity analysis. Model form uncertainty is an epistemic gap not addressed in this assessment."
